\c 62 Kunyarara kwomweya womunhu anovimba naMwari Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomutoo waJedhutuni. Pisarema raDhavhidhi. 62I Zvirokwazvo, mweya wangu unongorindira Mwari; Kwaari ndiko kunobva kuponeswa kwangu. 2 Ndiye oga dombo rangu nomuponesi wangu; Ndiye shongwe yangu yakakwirira; handingazununguswi zvikuru. 3 Muchavavarira munhu kusvikira riniko, Kuti mumuuraye imi mose, Sorusvingo runoda kuwa, noruzhowa runotseyama? 4 Vanongorangana kuti vamusundire pasi abve paukuru hwake; Vanofarira nhema; Vanoropafadza nomuromo wavo, asi vanotuka mumwoyo mavo. 5 Mweya wangu, rindira Mwari zvirokwa7NO; Nokuti ndinomutarira iye. 6 Ndiye oga dombo rangu noruponeso rwangu; Ndiye shongwe yangu yakakwirira; handingazununguswi.
